{"id": 1031, "genre": 1001, "title": "在你身上有怎样的“冷感”特质？", "description": "冷感：知道却不愿意追随所谓新潮时尚的东西，快看我的冷漠脸。（题图来自：AGEN­TUR AZUR）", "record_count": 11295, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152309bSd8HJj4MO01DtIF.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-22T11:04:20Z", "options": [{"id": 91392, "content": "连下载新的毛片的兴致都没了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523818}, {"id": 91648, "content": "不看余罪?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511676}, {"id": 93440, "content": "大家都在健身减肥秀身材，而我还在一日三餐不节食。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659298}, {"id": 91649, "content": "余罪 太子妃啥都没看过", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570582}, {"id": 91394, "content": "什么618双11双12 不想买的时候管你打几折", "image": null, "praise_count": 266, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563799}, {"id": 91650, "content": "《星你》至今没看完?，等一下，全名叫啥玩意？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654149}, {"id": 93442, "content": "就是喜欢一个人吃饭睡觉逛街看电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659286}, {"id": 91651, "content": "从未在6.18 11.11 12.12 这些日子网购过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654152}, {"id": 91396, "content": "我不需要的都没兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645928}, {"id": 91652, "content": "喜欢半夜4点一个人在家乡小城戴着耳机量马路，感觉无比自由舒畅；钻研很多兴趣门类里的一小类，吉他只弹antoine dufour，摄影只星空摄影，歌曲只听post-rock；PS：每个都是真爱，绝不装逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471620}, {"id": 91397, "content": "我认为最好的生活就是没有手机，没有电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645928}, {"id": 91654, "content": "没觉得aj好看 会不会被世界遗弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155086}, {"id": 91655, "content": "很多朋友，偏偏喜欢聚会的时候发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650378}, {"id": 91400, "content": "有话说，有屁放。最讨厌有人发给：在吗？回他：什么事。然后杳无音讯，我不care，也不好奇你到底要说什么，只是觉得我回复的那句“什么事”，简直是在浪费我的时间，还好只是简单的三个字，连标点符号都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620551}, {"id": 91656, "content": "从不看《花千骨》之类的超能力古装片", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589842}, {"id": 91401, "content": "大家都在炫跑步，炫健身，我就不?", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627195}, {"id": 91657, "content": "个人感觉美剧好无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654176}, {"id": 92425, "content": "就算是我欣赏的偶像演的电视剧，但是剧情烂，我也不看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619967}, {"id": 91658, "content": "天生拒绝一切低俗物的心态！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654183}, {"id": 91403, "content": "从来不下表情包", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613988}, {"id": 91659, "content": "就不看跑男，无聊至极不知道亮点在哪里……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174091}, {"id": 91404, "content": "艺人怎样关我什么事儿，我只是喜欢看他的脸啊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564398}, {"id": 91405, "content": "基本不看朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117975}, {"id": 91661, "content": "和任何人说话绝不超过十句，每句不超过五个字，哥就是这么任性", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640155}, {"id": 99853, "content": "在全班同学都玩王者荣耀时也没准备玩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684681}, {"id": 94222, "content": "更喜欢一个人的大学生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663214}, {"id": 104206, "content": "不看网剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 91407, "content": "不喜欢真人秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 91663, "content": "做自己感兴趣的事情，无论它有多么冷门。不参与觉得无聊的事情，无论它的舆论热度有多高。", "image": "img/option/option/201607021828179ED7S0gnLAyj6t4i.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654199}, {"id": 91408, "content": "不喜欢在qq，微信一些聊天软件上聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653333}, {"id": 91664, "content": "不喜欢搭班一起吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582056}, {"id": 91409, "content": "不看奔跑吧兄弟", "image": null, "praise_count": 654, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 544761}, {"id": 91665, "content": "有很多人喜欢的我就不喜欢了，就享受发现小众事物的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637721}, {"id": 93201, "content": "不想买狗链子，因为人脖一条", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658298}, {"id": 91410, "content": "对流行完全无感", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653340}, {"id": 91666, "content": "看魔兽 周围人大喊大叫 我睡着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651573}, {"id": 91411, "content": "对流行敬而远之", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653340}, {"id": 91667, "content": "几年前还喜欢看湖南卫视，现在连电视都懒得开了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626531}, {"id": 91412, "content": "除了工作和事先定好的约会 其他时间基本都在家宅着 就算网上没东西可看了 就算睡觉也不想出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613815}, {"id": 91668, "content": "人脉是什么东东？能吃吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644625}, {"id": 91413, "content": "关了朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653343}, {"id": 91669, "content": "不玩游戏，不看直播，不玩朋友圈……喜欢独自一人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651208}, {"id": 91414, "content": "从前喜欢的明星突然爆红后就不喜欢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635647}, {"id": 91670, "content": "别人喜欢的都不喜欢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464524}, {"id": 92694, "content": "不理睬无油盐的话与不在乎的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657007}, {"id": 91415, "content": "思考了很久，才想回答這個問題……", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422655}, {"id": 91671, "content": "我几乎很少发朋友圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653241}, {"id": 91416, "content": "新款球鞋再好看不符合老子审美照样也不买帐", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139752}, {"id": 91672, "content": "绝对不凑热闹，排队的餐馆和买的东西，绝对不去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384836}, {"id": 91418, "content": "天气热了，都在开空调，我坚决只吹电扇～", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644855}]}